import React from 'react'
import { Row, Col, Image, ListGroup, Button, Card } from 'react-bootstrap';

const Contact = () => {
    return (
    <Row className='mt-5'>
        
        <Col md={6} xs={12} className='text-center'>
            <Card>
                <Card.Body>
                    <Image src={'images/b-link-p.jpg'} roundedCircle responsive alt='besart' className='profile-image mb-3' />
                    <ListGroup>
                        <ListGroup.Item action>Besart Mullabazi</ListGroup.Item>
                        <ListGroup.Item action>FullStack Developer</ListGroup.Item>
                        <ListGroup.Item action>Morbi leo risus</ListGroup.Item>
                        <ListGroup.Item action>Porta ac consectetur ac</ListGroup.Item>
                        <ListGroup.Item action>Vestibulum at eros</ListGroup.Item>
                    </ListGroup>
                </Card.Body>
            </Card>
        </Col>
            
        <Col md={6} xs={12}>
            <Image src={'images/b-link-p.jpg'} roundedCircle responsive alt='besart' className='profile-image' />
        </Col>
        
    </Row>
    )
}

export default Contact
